These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Hobby: singing, skydiving, gardening, puzzles
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Hobby:singing is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Hobby:skydiving##2
4. Hobby:puzzles is on the far left##1
5. Hobby:gardening is between Hobby:skydiving and Hobby:singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | puzzles         | skydiving   | gardening | singing       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
