2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Game:scrabble is on the right of Game:snooker##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Game:snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Game   | billiard    | backgammon   | snooker | scrabble       |

