Sport: skiing, snowboarding, golf, skateboarding
1. Sport:golf is on the right of Food:kale##1
2. Sport:golf is between Sport:snowboarding and Food:corn##2
3. Sport:snowboarding is on the far left##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Sport:skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Sport   | snowboarding | golf   | skateboarding | skiing |

